comments.body:
[~dkavanagh]: I'm with [~viglesias] that we should support clchost in 4.2, and we should log a deprecation warning (in console.log) when clchost/clcport are used, perhaps with the following wording...

{code}
The 'clchost' and 'clcport' settings are deprecated as of the 4.2 release and will be removed in 4.3.  Please use 'ufshost' and 'ufsport' instead.
{code}
